lyrics:
Beneath the city lights, dreams take flight,
(2) Freedom in the air, shining just as bright.
(3) Streets alive with stories, never to be told,
(4) In the heart of the city, a melody unfolds.

(5) Sunset whispers secrets, memories align,
(6) This American dream, every moment, divine.
(7) Dancing with the sunrise, singing through the night,
(8) Love in America, an endless, timeless light.
